  "title": "🦅 Junior Sales and Marketing",
  "description": "<p>Our company is expanding and we want YOU!</p>\n<p>At Euphoria organisation we are a bunch of dynamic individuals who works towards being the leader in the sales &amp; marketing industry. We work closely with MNCs in the market locally and overseas. We believe that our people are our greatest asset. Here, we focus on developing each and every individual from personal to business skills and we do our best to see everyone coming in &amp; out with happiness.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>🫶🏻Description:</p>\n<p>On-site sales &amp; operation</p>\n<p>Improve client’s branding &amp; achieving sales targets</p>\n<p>Manage &amp; lead a sales &amp; marketing team</p>\n<p>Market our client product and services through business development</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>🤩What you can look forward to:</p>\n<p>Overseas exposure &amp; travelling</p>\n<p>Leadership skills development</p>\n<p>Transparent advancement structure</p>\n<p>Personal development workshops</p>\n<p>Young, fun &amp; positive team environment</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>🎯What are we looking for:</p>\n<p>Keen learning attitude</p>\n<p>Driven for success &amp; progress</p>\n<p>Outgoing</p>\n<p>No experience needed</p>\n<p>Just 1 minute click &amp; it may change your career path</p>",
